-----------------------------------------

Welcome back to The Daily Courant, your pocket guide to Puck=E2=80=99s best
new reporting.

=C2=A0

First up today, Dylan Byers assesses the anxieties of the political media c=
lass at the dawn of the second Trump era. Despite the genuflecting from bil=
lionaires and C.E.O.s toward the president-elect, the harsh realities of th=
e journalism business remain incredibly complex. So what=E2=80=99s actually=
 needed for legacy media institutions to endure?=C2=A0

=C2=A0

